column16: Eduardo Nunez singles on a soft ground ball to second baseman Jason Kipnis.   Miguel Sano to 3rd.    Eddie Rosario to 2nd.
Eddie Rosario singles on a ground ball to right fielder Jerry Sands.   Miguel Sano to 2nd.
Yoenis Cespedes grounds out, shortstop Mike Aviles to first baseman Carlos Santana.
Miguel Cabrera doubles (12) on a fly ball to center fielder Michael Brantley.   Ian Kinsler scores.
Ian Kinsler singles on a soft line drive to left fielder Ryan Raburn.
Rajai Davis grounds out, third baseman Giovanny Urshela to first baseman Carlos Santana.
